	<message label="003" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Surprised" target="actor" targetSpec="" />咦咦！<delay20 />我身上有跳蚤！？<delay40 />
<anim id="SadSpiral" target="actor" targetSpec="" />而且居然還讓男生跟我說才發現，<delay20 />
