	<message label="004" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="TakenAback" target="actor" targetSpec="" />呀！<delay40 />
<anim id="Frantic" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我居然完全沒注意到<delay20 />身上有跳蚤！<delay40 />
