	<message label="005" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Surprised" target="actor" targetSpec="" />咦！？<delay20 /><anim id="Worried" target="actor" targetSpec="" />雖然我是覺得身體癢癢的，<delay8 />
